  infoCursor: Gas -2
  infoDescription: 'Circling around looking for the hotel 3 times

    because the
    sign was too small.'
  descriptionVariants:
  - "Drove past the gas station because \nI was too busy taking pictures of the view.\nGas
    -2"
  - 'GPS led me down an unpaved road.

    Gas -2'
  - "Circling around looking for \nthe hotel 3 times because \nthe sign was too small.\nGas
    -2"
  - "Stopped at every photo spot, \neven a utility pole.\nGas -2"
  - "Took a \u201Cshortcut\u201D that actually made the drive longer.\nGas -2"
  - "Drove past my destination because \nI was too busy singing along to the music.\nGas
    -2"
  - "Stopped to buy coffee, \nbut my friend took 40 minutes \nto take pictures.\nGas
    -2"
  - "Turned on the AC while \nwaiting for my friend to wake up, \nDrained away the
    fuel.\nGas -2"
  - "Got lost and ended up \nin the wrong village.\nGas -2"
  - 'Stuck in traffic because

    someone was taking pictures

    in the middle
    of the road.

    Gas -2'
  isGoal: 0
  isImpassable: 0
